node.text:
I was in DC yesterday to be a guest on ‘The Miraculous Life Podcast’. I was able to get some really great practical tips out on how to deal with a ‘runaway mind’. It’s a great episode. Check it out wherever you get your podcast. 
Then toured the nation’s capital for a bit with 
In the evening we had some amazing Indian food served by an elderly man I think may be enlightened!
I tend to think everybody is enlightened because everybody is! 😂
The light shines through us when we are relaxed, the mind is quiet and the heart is open. •
•
